  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic implant stress-shielding credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite element analysis (FEA) prediction of periprosthetic bone remodeling and stress-shielding in a cementless total hip arthroplasty stem. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative changes in bone mineral density (BMD) distribution at 12 months post-implantation for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed on material property inputs. Decision: Accepted.",
