      "rationale": "Code verification performed using method of manufactured solutions (MMS) for the bone remodeling constitutive equations. Spatial convergence confirmed with theoretical second-order accuracy. Results compared against NAFEMS benchmark LE10 and orthopedic-specific benchmarks from Prendergast et al. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2 for MRL 3."
