      "rationale": "Cadaveric test conditions are documented including specimen age, sex, BMI, bone mineral density (T-score), preservation method, and storage temperature. Loading fixture configuration matches ASTM F2996 guidance for femoral stem testing. Environmental conditions (temperature, humidity) during mechanical testing are recorded. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2 for MRL 3."
    },
