      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metrics defined a priori: mean absolute error (MAE) and root mean square error (RMSE) for BMD change per Gruen zone, and Pearson correlation coefficient. Validation dashboard includes 95% confidence intervals on experimental measurements. All predicted values fall within experimental uncertainty bands. Bayesian model comparison score computed. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
