      "rationale": "The primary QOI (percent BMD change per Gruen zone at 12 months) directly corresponds to the clinical endpoint used in post-market surveillance DXA studies. Secondary QOIs (cortical strain, stem micromotion) are mapped to regulatory acceptance criteria in the predicate device 510(k) summary. QOI relevance matrix linking model outputs to clinical endpoints is documented. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
