      "rationale": "Validation activities span cadaveric mechanical testing, CT-based morphological validation, and gait load boundary condition verification — all directly relevant to the COU of predicting in vivo bone remodeling. Validation specimens bracket the intended patient population in age and BMD. A validation relevance matrix explicitly maps each validation study to the COU assumptions and model features. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
