      "rationale": "Iterative convergence of the nonlinear bone remodeling solver verified: residual force norm below 1×10⁻⁵ N at each remodeling time step. Newton-Raphson iteration history documented for all 3 activity profile cases. Round-off error estimated via double-precision arithmetic analysis; negligible relative to discretization error. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
