      "rationale": "Simulation workflow is governed by a controlled simulation plan document (SPD-ORT-2024-003) reviewed by an independent analyst. Input deck review checklist completed and signed. Boundary condition application verified by independent re-run on a subset of cases. User qualification records on file for all analysts who executed production simulations. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
