      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-orth-ac-modelform",
      "rationale": "The Huiskes strain-adaptive bone remodeling algorithm is selected based on systematic literature review of 14 candidate remodeling theories. Model form assumptions (isotropic remodeling, lazy zone threshold, remodeling rate constant) are documented with supporting references. Sensitivity analysis on remodeling rate constant (±30%) shows QOI variation of less than 6% in all Gruen zones. Model form uncertainty included in overall uncertainty budget. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
