      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed on 8 key material property inputs (cortical Young's modulus, cancellous apparent density-modulus relationship coefficients, Poisson's ratios, implant Ti-6Al-4V properties) using 5000 Latin hypercube samples. Input probability distributions derived from published nanoindentation and mechanical testing datasets. Resulting 95% prediction intervals on BMD change QOIs reported for all Gruen zones. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
